      "value": "<p><b>Element</b> fire; <b>Type</b> utility (Sp); <b>Level</b> 3; <b>Burn</b> 0<br><b>Saving Throw</b> Fortitude negates; see text; <b>SR</b> no</p>\n<p>You transform a source of open flame within 120 feet into a cloud of choking smoke, filling a 20-foot-radius spread and affecting vision like a smokestick. All creatures that begin their turns inside the area become sickened as long as they remain in the smoke and for 1d4+1 rounds thereafter (Fortitude negates).</p>"
